{
  "id": "adv_card_suz_51_02",
  "title": "成宮すず 2話 すずにゃんお姫様計画",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_living-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_living-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――すずの誕生祭一週間前",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――One week before Suzu’s birthday festival",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_02-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "事務所で誕生祭の打ち合わせ終わったって、連絡あった\nそろそろすずちゃん……寮に戻って来る、かも……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Suzu messaged that the meeting for her birthday festival at the office is over.\nSuzu-chan… might be heading back to the dorm soon…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.7666659913,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_02-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣ちゃん、すずにゃんお姫様計画……\nちゃんと、覚えてる……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mei-chan‚ do you remember\nthe Suzu-nyan princess plan…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.6666659913,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_02-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "任せて！　まずは敬語を使うでしょ？\nそれと紅茶を差し出す！　……後は、なんだっけ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Leave it to me! First‚ we use honorifics‚\nand offer her tea! …What was next again?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.433332658,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_02-szk003.m4a",
      "text": "お菓子パーティー、する……\nさらに私厳選の、アイドルのDVDを観てもらう……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We’ll have a snack party…\nAnd let her watch my carefully selected collection of idol DVDs…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.3666659913,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_02-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "最後は極上リラックスタイムだったよね\nうん、大丈夫！　芽衣覚えたよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Lastly‚ we give her the ultimate relaxation experience!\nYeah‚ it’s all coming back to me! I’ve got it‚ Mei.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.3666659913,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_02-szk004.m4a",
      "text": "でも、一番大事なのは……\n自然にお姫様気分を味わってもらうこと……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But‚ the most important thing is…\nTo make her naturally feel like a princess…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.5333321494,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_02-szk005.m4a",
      "text": "そのために……全力で、おもてなししよう……\nすずちゃんが来たら……ミッション、スタート……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So to do that… Let's give her our best hospitality…\nWhen Suzu-chan gets here… The mission starts…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.599998816,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4521.154944299994,
          "startTime": 60.1211537603
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4833.334517299995,
          "startTime": 60.4333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_02-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "事前に決めることが沢山あるんですのね……\n時間は限られてますし、もうひと頑張りですわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There are so many things to decide beforehand…\nTime is limited‚ I need to work even harder!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.3630592268,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_02-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "すずにゃん様のおなーーりーー！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Suzunyan-sama has arrived!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.4532607958,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_02-szk006.m4a",
      "text": "ははーっ……って\nそれ、お姫様じゃなくてお殿様……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah… What?\nThat's for a young master‚ not a princess…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.0333349468,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_02-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "ええっ！？　一体なんなんですの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh!? What’s going on?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.0083720611,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_02-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "これはね～！\nすずにゃんお姫様計画――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This is~!\nThe Suzu-nyan princess plan――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.4666733665,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_02-szk007.m4a",
      "text": "すずにゃん様、お、お紅茶はいかがですか……っ！\n誕生祭の準備で……喉、渇いてない……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Suzunyan-sama‚ w-would you like some tea……!\nYou must be thirsty… from preparing for your birthday festival…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.0000148379,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_02-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "はあ……まあ、確かに\nちょっと休憩したかったところですけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well… It’s true\nI was hoping to take a break…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.4890636525,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_02-szk008.m4a",
      "text": "私達も、ちょうど紅茶、飲みたかった、よね……\n芽衣ちゃん……ね、そうだよね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We were just thinking about having some tea ourselves…\nMei-chan… Right…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.1000112775,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_02-mei005.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうそう！　そうだったそうだった！\nすずにゃん様、一緒にお紅茶飲みましょう！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "R-right! That’s right‚ that’s right!\nSuzu-nyan-sama‚ let’s have some tea together!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.400009243,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_02-szk009.m4a",
      "text": "アッサム、ダージリン、フレーバーティー……\nいろいろ、ある……ます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Assam‚ Darjeeling‚ flavored tea…\nWe have a variety…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.8666759096,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_02-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "あら、それじゃあダージリンティーを……って\nごまかさないでくださいまし。何か様子が変ですわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well then‚ I’ll have some Darjeeling tea… Wait a minute.\nDon’t try to fool me. Something’s up.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.25429612,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_02-mei006.m4a",
      "text": "そんなことないよ～\nね、芽衣達、普通だよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Nothing’s up~\nRight? We’re acting normal‚ aren’t we?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 134.0000082257,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-03.m4a",
          "delay": 9733.325107600023,
          "startTime": 143.7333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_02-szk010.m4a",
      "text": "うん……どこも、おかしく、ない……\n紅茶が淹れ終わるまで、このお菓子、どうぞ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Y-yeah… There’s nothing strange…\nHere‚ have some snacks while the tea’s brewing…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.1666789614,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_02-mei007.m4a",
      "text": "怜ちゃんオススメのマカロンだよ\nみんなでお菓子パーティーしよーっ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "These are the macarons Rei recommended.\nLet’s have a snack party~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 147.1000122948,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_02-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "お菓子パーティーって……でも美味しそうですわね\nそちらのマカロンは何味がありますの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A snack party…? But these macarons look delicious.\nWhat flavors do you have?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 155.3019426744,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_02-mei009.m4a",
      "text": "ベリー系とレモン、チョコに抹茶、ナッツにバナナ……\nそれからキャラメル……い～～っぱいあるよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We have berries‚ lemon‚ chocolate‚ matcha‚ nuts‚ banana…\nand caramel… We’ve got tons!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 162.6333456281,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_02-suz006.m4a",
      "text": "それでは、チョコ味をいただきますわね\nもぐもぐ……ん～っ、美味しいですわ～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well then‚ I’ll have the chocolate one.\nMunch‚ munch… Mmm! Delicious!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 170.1872295142,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_02-szk011.m4a",
      "text": "ティータイムには……これがオススメ……\n私が厳選した……雫コレクション……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "For teatime… I recommend this…\nMy personally curated… Shizuku collection…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 180.0000153466,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_02-suz007.m4a",
      "text": "こ、これは……！　いろんなアイドルの\nバースデーイベントのみを集めたDVD！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "T-this is…! A DVD compilation\nof just birthday events!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 187.2927058936,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_02-szk012.m4a",
      "text": "すずちゃん、様の……好みに合うように\nブレンドした、一品です……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I blended this together… to suit your tastes‚\nSuzuchan-sama…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 194.7000214502,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
